---
title: Seared Salmon & Leek-Lemon Sauce with Creamy Potato Mash & Hazelnut Crumb
description: Seared pink salmon has got to be the fanciest of the fish in the sea, elegant and fresh and we love a nutty crumb to
add a touch of the earth. The addition of a leek and zesty lemon sauce keeps the salmon at the top of this popularity ladder. It will also quickly become a favourite at the table too!

